data.description:
Beautiful spacious home in great neighborhood and in the heart of wine country!
This spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features a full kitchen with updated appliances, including a gas range. Cozy living room, and a nook upstairs that would make for a great office space or play area.
Great storage space with plenty of closets. Separate laundry room with washer and dryer hook ups.
Master bedroom has lots of natural light, and includes a master bathroom.
Large fenced back yard with great patio space. This home also includes a 2 car garage! 

Quick commute to 99W.

Come check it out to see if this could be the perfect home for you!

Monthly rent $2,500
Security deposit $2,000
Dogs ok on a case by case basis with additional $250 deposit.
No Smoking

Tenant is responsible for all utilities including yard maintenance for the front and back yard. Owner has provided lawn mower and yard tools.
